introduction: Mudd afus i tifin n temsisɣal i yimagraden n Wikipedia!
instructions_goal: Tukkist n tengalt Wikipedia ddaw-a ur tettwaɣbel ara sɣuṛ {link_start}aɣbalu aɣelsan{link_end}. Tzemreḍ ad tafeḍ yiwet?
instructions_details: Sit ɣef %s akken ad tedduḍ ar Wikipedia sakin ad tseɣtiḍ aḥric n tengalt neɣ %s akken ad walin wayeḍ. Wali %s ma yella ɣur-k isteqsiyen. Afud igarrzen!
lead_section_hint: Aḍris-agi d tukkist n uqeṛṛu n umagrad : ɣas akken ma terniḍ timsisɣal d afrayan. Wali %s u wugar n telɣut.
beginners_hint: Ur teẓriḍ ara amek ara ternuḍ tanebdurt? Wali %s.
page_not_found_text: Asebter i tettwaliḍ ur yezgi yella — ahat tanebdurt-agi tettwaf yakan ? Uɣal ar %s akken ad teẓreḍ ugar!
footer: %s yettwag sɣuṛ iwiziwen, yezdeɣ di %s udiɣ yettwasuqel s %s.
